Company Overview of Abom, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Abom, Inc. designs and develops snow goggle with active anti-fog technology. Its product has a metal film in the lens that heats up to deter condensation. The company was incorporated in 2014 and is based in Portland, Oregon.


7155 SW Varns StreetPortland, OR 97223United StatesFounded in 2014



Phone: 844-246-2266

Fax: 503-521-7453

